(53, 3, 303, 'The utmost luxury experience in Puerto Ju\r\n\r\nIn the Presidential Suite, you can even enjoy your own private seaside pool! This is the hotel’s biggest and most elegant room, with 1239 sq ft split between a large bedroom with a king-size bed and a spacious living room with separate dining room and kitchen. You can have breakfast on the large terrace with direct access to the beach while listening to the waves breaking on the shore or watching your favorite show on the SmartTV. The bathroom features twin sinks and a shower.', 2, 0, 19, 2, 1, 0, '1050.00', NULL, '2019-11-27 09:36:53', '2019-12-11 17:59:22'),
