(59, 3, 404, 'For those looking for something vast and modern\r\n\r\nTake advantage of vast new spaces in the Junior Deluxe Suite with a bedroom and living room and the comfort that comes from being in a refurbished area in the closest part of the complex to the ocean. They also come with their own concierge service where our staff will attend to your every need throughout your stay.', 1, 0, 25, 1, 0, 0, '480.00', NULL, '2019-11-27 09:36:53', '2019-12-11 18:03:03'),
(60, 3, 405, 'For those looking for more exclusivity\r\n\r\nThe Oceanfront Rooftop Corner Junior Suite is the most remarkable room in the entire hotel. From the rooftop pool, you’ll be able to take in unparalleled panoramic views of Cancún’s beaches. This spacious room, located on the hotel’s top floor, has all of the details to make your stay unforgettable. This well-appointed room features a premium minibar, smart TV, and spacious bathroom with bathtub and shower. You’ll also enjoy the convenience of a butler service at the hotel beach and pool, as well as room service, access to SPA Sensation’s hydrotherapy area, and wine pairing courses—all of which will make your vacation simply unforgettable. ', 2, 0, 22, 2, 0, 1, '1500.00', NULL, '2019-11-27 09:36:53', '2019-12-11 18:04:44'),
(61, 2, 102, 'For guests who want to be near the beach\r\n\r\nThe Superior Double room is located in the most coveted area of the hotel, offering you a retreat just steps away from the Caribbean waters. You can also spend time soaking in the SPA Sensations hydrotherapy pools, where you’ll enjoy complimentary access. You’ll also be able to take advantage of private check-in, beach towels in your room, and tons of other amenities that will make your vacation in the Dominican Republic an experience to remember.', 3, 2, 18, 2, 0, 1, '410.00', '2019-12-05 01:39:24', '2019-12-05 00:12:46', '2019-12-11 18:03:31');
